11:23.557 --> 11:26.686
that leads to kidney failure,
lung failure and things like that.

11:27.520 --> 11:31.232
<i>There was a patient who was a senator</i>
<i>from Brazil.</i>

11:31.357 --> 11:33.734
<i>He didn't speak any English and I said,</i>

11:33.818 --> 11:35.778
<i>"Well, I can't have a conversation</i>
<i>with this guy,</i>

