<i>and I saw this... article...</i>

14:10.516 --> 14:14.645
<i>in a publication called </i>MMWR.

14:14.895 --> 14:21.360
Morbidity and Mortality Weekly Report.
<i>And it reported five men...</i>

14:21.819 --> 14:28.325
curiously all gay men, who developed
a very strange pneumonia

14:28.701 --> 14:30.578
called pneumocystis pneumonia.

14:30.828 --> 14:34.790
And, being a busy young investigator
at the time,

14:35.082 --> 14:39.295
I took it, I put it in my desk
and I said, "This must be a fluke.

14:39.420 --> 14:40.713
