1:34:51.727 --> 1:34:55.898
DR. FAUCI:<i> What the NIH has accomplished,</i>
<i>can accomplish and will accomplish,</i>

1:34:56.482 --> 1:34:59.819
to me, that's the embodiment
of the American spirit.

1:35:00.695 --> 1:35:05.825
<i>The experience that you can do anything</i>
<i>if you put your mind to it, anything.</i>

