1:40:21.765 --> 1:40:27.146
<i>"between viruses'</i>
<i>spectacular genetic capability,</i>

1:40:27.229 --> 1:40:28.731
<i>"and our wits."</i>

1:40:38.365 --> 1:40:40.951
<i>As someone at my age</i>
<i>and my stage in life,</i>

