<i>it's natural to look ahead and say,</i>

1:40:44.288 --> 1:40:46.790
<i>"What are my children</i>
<i>gonna be faced with?"</i>

1:40:48.042 --> 1:40:51.587
And the one thing I can hope for...
really hope for,

1:40:52.171 --> 1:40:57.468
is that emerging infections
don't inevitably become pandemics.

1:41:01.847 --> 1:41:05.517
<i>I am optimistic that the lessons</i>
<i>that we've learned</i>

1:41:06.310 --> 1:41:08.020
<i>will prevent that from happening.</i>

1:41:15.694 --> 1:41:18.238
<i>I hope that if historians look back...</i>

1:41:19.114 --> 1:41:22.076
if they ever would wanna look back...
(LAUGHS)

1:41:22.576 --> 1:41:25.287
<i>...at what I've done, and my life.</i>

